# @[❮](https://aelobdog.github.io/aelobdog-writes) New Blog Tool
#### 07-07-2021

I just spent about an hour or two reworking my blog tool. The new version, @[lih2](https://github.com/aelobdog/lih2) is much better than what I was using before. Lih2 is a shell script, instead of a Go program that @[lih](https://github.com/aelobdog/lih) was. It now automatically generates the blog with the posts ordered, latest first. It also "recompiles" the blog index and all the blog posts, which means that making a small change somewhere in one blog post gets incorporated into the blog naturally without needing any manual intervention like lih did.

So what's changed ? lih2,
   - /automatically orders posts (latest on top)/
   - /automatically incorporates changes made to posts/
   - /allows deletion of blog posts by moving a file out of the 'posts' directory/
   - /allows renaming of blog posts by changing filename of post/

That's it for now !
